      "rationale": "Validation experiments used the nominal FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry with the same impeller-volute clearances as the COU device. Operating envelope (2500–3500 rpm; 3–6 L/min) spans the 5 COU operating points. Fluid analogue viscosity and density match physiological blood within 5%. Geometric and dynamic similarity criteria are documented in the validation plan."
