    "id": "https://uofa.net/morrison/decision/cou1-cpb-accepted-2026",
    "type": "DecisionRecord",
    "actor": "https://uofa.net/morrison/actor/credibility-assessment-team",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. The six non-assessed factors are appropriately scoped out at this risk level. The assessment team reviewed the dataVintage discrepancy between the primary experimental hemolysis dataset (2025-10-14T00:00:00Z) and the model revision date (2025-11-03T00:00:00Z) and concluded that the intervening mesh-topology refinement — which adjusted near-wall cell layering in the volute tongue region — did not alter the fluid boundary conditions, rotational speed setpoints, or material property inputs against which the experimental data were collected. On this basis the team judged the dataset to remain representative of the revised model build and accepted the package without a formal re-validation study against the updated mesh. The decision is recorded here for traceability.",
